vedi ( english : firecracker ) is a 2011 tamil action-thriller film directed by prabhu deva featuring vishal and sameera reddy in the lead roles . a remake of the successful 2008 telugu film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , the film was released on 30 september 2011 across 250 screens in tamil nadu , 62 screens in kerala and 28 screens in karnataka vedi received mixed reviews , but ended up as a commercial success at the box office . it has been dubbed in hindi as the fighter &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; no. 1 .